OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,FFour members of an Albanian crime gang
OL,8,Fhave been jailed for their parts in a
OL,9,Fburglary spree that saw 44 homes
OL,10,Frobbed across the UK.
OL,12,FThe gang are thought to have stolen
OL,13,Fmore than #1 million worth of goods
OL,14,Fbetween March 2024 and March 2025
OL,15,Facross Cheshire, Nottinghamshire,
OL,16,FCleveland, Derbyshire, Leicestershire,
OL,17,FNottinghamshire, Staffordshire,
OL,18,FWarwickshire and the West Midlands.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
