OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,FThe thieves would climb through first
OL,8,Ffloor windows to look for jewellery,
OL,9,Fdesigner handbags, watches and cash.
OL,11,FKristian Gropcaj, 30, George Pepa, 31,
OL,12,FKrisjian Dedndreaj, 28, and Sidorjan
OL,13,FLleshi, 26, were all jailed for a
OL,14,Fcombined 38 years.
OL,16,FAlong with them, a British woman from
OL,17,FWalsall was spared jail and handed a
OL,18,Fsuspended sentence for possession of
OL,19,Fcriminal property.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,FEndrit Nikolli, 27, is awaiting
OL,8,Fsentencing.
OL,10,FDuring the sentencing hearing, the
OL,11,Fcourt heard a statement from one of
OL,12,Ftheir victims from Macclesfield, who
OL,13,Fsaid the burglaries have "shaken the
OL,14,Ffoundation and security in our family."
OL,16,FThey said: "The realisation that
OL,17,Fstrangers had broken into our house
OL,18,Fwhile we were inside - just a floor
OL,19,Faway, was something I will never
OL,20,Fforget.
OL,26,@xD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,F"We didn't know if they were armed,
OL,8,Fhow many people there were, or whether
OL,9,Fthey would come downstairs, meaning we
OL,10,Fwere forced to barricade ourselves in
OL,11,Fthe lounge."
OL,13,FThe victim said the burglars took
OL,14,Fsentimental items, jewellery and
OL,15,Fwatches were family heirlooms.
OL,17,FThey said: "Since the burglary, I've
OL,18,Fstruggled to feel comfortable in my
OL,19,Fhome.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@LO]yD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,F"I constantly worry about whether we
OL,8,Fare safe, whether someone is watching
OL,9,Fus, and whether something like this
OL,10,Fcould happen again."
OL,12,FThe homeowner finished their impact
OL,13,Fstatement saying: "The effects of this
OL,14,Fcrime go far beyond the physical loss
OL,15,Fof property.
OL,17,F"It has affected how we live, how we
OL,18,Fsleep, how we feel in our home, and
OL,19,Fhow we move forward."
OL,26,@rD@TO]uD@SOUyD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,FThe investigation into the gang began
OL,8,Fin October 2024 when detectives at
OL,9,FMacclesfield Proactive CID became
OL,10,Faware of a series of burglaries across
OL,11,Fthe eastern area of Cheshire,
OL,12,Fincluding incidents in Macclesfield,
OL,13,FPrestbury, Weston and Willaston.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Dave
OL,16,FWorthington said: "We had Nikolli that
OL,17,Fwas identified through a DNA hit. We
OL,18,Fhad to make a decision whether we
OL,19,Farrested that one individual for one
OL,20,Fburglary or do we make this a more
OL,21,Fjoined-up investigation.
OL,26,@xD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,F"This was about disrupting and
OL,8,Fdismantling the whole crime group and
OL,9,Fthat's what we've done in this case."
OL,11,FThe eight high-profile burglaries in
OL,12,FCheshire were linked to others across
OL,13,Fthe UK by footwear marks left at the
OL,14,Fscenes.
OL,16,FPolice found a red Ford Focus insured
OL,17,Fto one of the burglary gang members
OL,18,FKristian Gropcaj was also present at
OL,19,Fmany of the incidents.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,FThe gang were also linked to two
OL,8,Fburglaries in Cleveland, nine in
OL,9,FDerbyshire, two in Leicestershire,
OL,10,Ffive in Nottinghamshire, seven in
OL,11,FStaffordshire, two in Warwickshire and
OL,12,Fnine in West Midlands.
OL,14,FTelephone records checks then found
OL,15,Fthat four men had been meeting on a
OL,16,Fregular basis at a coffee shop in the
OL,17,FJewellery Quarter in Birmingham.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,FOn 2 July 2025, detectives arrested
OL,8,FNikolli, Lleshaj, Gropcaj and Tubb
OL,9,Fafter they raided homes in Walsall,
OL,10,FSutton Coldfield and Birmingham. Some
OL,11,F13 designer handbags and 14 watches
OL,12,Fworth almost #17,000 were also
OL,13,Frecovered.
OL,15,FBut the vast majority of the burgled
OL,16,Fitems, expected to total #1 million,
OL,17,Fhad been sold on or melted down before
OL,18,Fthe police raid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Dave
OL,8,FWorthington said there are a number of
OL,9,Fitems they recovered which they
OL,10,Fpresume stolen who they cannot trace
OL,11,Fthe owners of.
OL,13,FHe asked people who had been the
OL,14,Fvictims of a first floor burglary in a
OL,15,Frural area in the last 12-18 months to
OL,16,Fcheck Cheshire Police's website and
OL,17,Fsee if they can identify any of their
OL,18,Fitems.
OL,20,FDedndreaj and Lleshi were later
OL,21,Farrested in Surrey and Sheffield.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
