OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,FFollowing the raids hundreds of mobile
OL,8,Fphone images of the stolen items,
OL,9,Falong with messages with links to
OL,10,FGoogle maps which matched the scene of
OL,11,Fthe burglaries were found on the
OL,12,Fsuspect's phones.
OL,14,FPolice found that Jade Tubb, aged 33,
OL,15,Fwas in a relationship with Endrit
OL,16,FNikolli. She pleaded guilty to
OL,17,Fconspiracy to possess criminal
OL,18,Fproperty on 7 January.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
