OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,FDetective Sergeant Laura Fox said:
OL,8,F"During the searches, we recovered
OL,9,Fletters between Nikolli and Tubb, in
OL,10,Fwhich the pair described themselves as
OL,11,F'Bonnie and Clyde', in reference to
OL,12,Fhow they were working together to
OL,13,Fconduct the burglaries.
OL,15,F"Throughout our investigation it has
OL,16,Fbeen clear that the gang had
OL,17,Fabsolutely no regard for the impact
OL,18,Fthat their offences would have on the
OL,19,Fvictims. Instead they regularly
OL,20,Fgloated about their crimes and shared
OL,21,Fimages of ill-gotten gains."
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
