FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776265867
OL,3,CGang jailed for almost 40 years after
OL,4,Cstealing a million pounds worth of
OL,5,Cgoods
OL,7,FKristian Gropcaj and George Pepa were
OL,8,Fboth jailed for 9 years for conspiracy
OL,9,Fto commit burglary. Gropcaj also
OL,10,Freceived a concurrent sentence of 5
OL,11,Fyears for conspiracy to possess
OL,12,Fcriminal property. Pepa received a 4
OL,13,Fand a half year concurrent sentence
OL,14,Ffor the same crime.
OL,16,FSidorjan Lleshi was jailed for 10
OL,17,Fyears and 9 months for conspiracy to
OL,18,Fcommit burglary, one count of burglary
OL,19,Fand conspiracy to possess criminal
OL,20,Fproperty.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
